Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.util

Class HashBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stuypulse.stuylib.util.HashBuilder
  • public final class HashBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to generate HashCodes by combining multiple different objects / types. The combining function is taken from boost, as it is a great hash combiner

    It also has static methods available if creating a new class is undesirable.
